    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DLC总计九个建筑外观，内含：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜火楼：重檐蔽日夺天工，炉火纯青萃精华。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工建筑-精华萃取器-胜火楼（珍绝）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >繁花锦系列：晓看红湿处，花重锦官城。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >农副建筑-花圃-繁花锦（极其稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商业建筑-花店-繁花锦（非常稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工建筑-水露店-繁花锦（稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >娱乐建筑-花鸟园-繁花锦（稀有）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水墨系列：正是江南好风景，落花时节又逢君。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商业建筑-扇庄-水墨（极其稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商业建筑-风筝店-水墨（非常稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商业建筑-伞行-水墨（非常稀有）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手工建筑-造纸坊-水墨（稀有）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>建筑外观使用方式：</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307450/extras/79121946e6e01bffacefc4409f8ddff5.avif?t=1738116791\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307450/extras_big/79121946e6e01bffacefc4409f8ddff5.avif?t=1738116791 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307450/extras/90d35b9f7a419bd868d4ef1dd840bc52.avif?t=1738116791\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307450/extras_big/90d35b9f7a419bd868d4ef1dd840bc52.avif?t=1738116791 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
